The '''Latvian Railways Cup''' ({{lang-lv|Latvijas Dzelzceļa kauss}}) is an annual traditional international [[ice hockey]] [[tournament]], with the participation of teams from the [[Kontinental Hockey League]].<ref>{{cite news|url=http://eng.belta.by/all_news/sport/HC-Dinamo-Minsk-to-take-part-in-Latvian-Railways-Cup_i_74300.html|title=HC Dinamo Minsk to take part in Latvian Railways Cup|date=10 July 2014|publisher= Belarusian Telegraph Agency|accessdate=1 September 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.lsm.lv/en/gallery/riigas-dinamo-parbaudes-spele-latvijas-dzelzcelja-kausa-izciinja.g23962/|title=Riga Dinamo scrimmage game for Latvian Railways Cup|date=26 August 2014|publisher=Public broadcasting of Latvia|accessdate=1 September 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://en.hockey.by/news/mass-media/5121.html|title=Latvian Railways Cup|date=August 30, 2013|publisher=Belarusian Ice Hockey Association|accessdate=1 September 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://en.atlant-mo.ru/calendar/archive/archive_20112012/low-2011/khl/lzd/|title=Latvian Railways Cup 2011|publisher=Atlant|accessdate=1 September 2014}}</ref> It is sponsored by [[Latvian Railways]].

