{{Refimprove|date=September 2014}} {{ Infobox football tournament | current = [[2018 Turkmenistan Cup]] | logo = | founded = 1993 | region = {{flagicon|TKM}} [[Turkmenistan]] ([[Football Association of Turkmenistan]]) | number of teams = varying | current champions = [[Köpetdag Aşgabat]] (7th) | most successful club = [[Köpetdag Aşgabat]] (7 times) | broadcasters = | motto = }}
The '''Turkmenistan Cup''' ({{lang-tk|Türkmenistanyň kubogy}}) is an annually held [[Football (soccer)|football]] tournament for [[Turkmenistan|Turkmen]] [[football club]]s and is the second most important national title in Turkmen football after the [[Ýokary Liga]] title.
The cup has been contested since 1993.
The competition's most successful performers are [[Köpetdag Aşgabat]] with 6 trophies, followed by [[FC Balkan]] with 4.
